{"tid":660871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【母親節】心意卡透露每日逼溫書 女兒控訴：恨死你","createTime":"2018-05-11T05:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T18:03:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9913bfcb9c13a498e89164b9b53eb3cdca56bb58","tid":660871,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T05:17:28.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】星期日就是母親節，不少子女都會寫心意卡向媽媽表達心意。近日網上流傳一張圖片，見到一張女兒寫給媽媽的母親節心意卡，童真的筆跡，但內容充滿控訴，上款致「惡毒的媽媽」，提到每日被逼溫習，更明言「恨死你」，更祝媽媽「母親節傷心」，引起網民討論。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在Facebook專頁「巴打絲打」上載圖片，見到一名女兒透過寫母親節心意卡，向媽媽控訴，心意卡上款已感受到女兒的憤怒，以「惡毒的媽媽」為上款，其後道出心中感受，「你天天叫我溫習，煩死人，恨死你，祝你母親節傷心」，旁邊亦畫上憤怒樣貌的圖案。<br />\n<br />\n網民看完心意卡後都表示心痛，「呢個媽媽要諗下係咪平時逼得個女太緊，關心多啲小朋友，俾佢放鬆一下，小朋友好多時發洩完就冇事㗎啦，唔需要放喺心」、「香港學生自殺率一直居高不下，唔係無原因㗎，唉」、「佢寫出嚟係好事，佢唔寫出嚟，你仲驚」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nrR3vJ7OLdiez2sPKOootQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180511a094420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnrR3vJ7OLdiez2sPKOootQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180511a094420.jpg&h=2fe5f7fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E7%AF%80-%E5%BF%83%E6%84%8F%E5%8D%A1%E9%80%8F%E9%9C%B2%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E9%80%BC%E6%BA%AB%E6%9B%B8-%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E6%8E%A7%E8%A8%B4-%E6%81%A8%E6%AD%BB%E4%BD%A0-014700487.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%258D%25A1%25E9%2580%258F%25E9%259C%25B2%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%2580%25BC%25E6%25BA%25AB%25E6%259B%25B8-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E6%2581%25A8%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BD%25A0-014700487.html&d=zWmZ7NaQiltFwnZhPmYJRHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f1577ff2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E7%AF%80-%E5%BF%83%E6%84%8F%E5%8D%A1%E9%80%8F%E9%9C%B2%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E9%80%BC%E6%BA%AB%E6%9B%B8-%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E6%8E%A7%E8%A8%B4-%E6%81%A8%E6%AD%BB%E4%BD%A0-014700487.html</a>"},{"pid":"af56239087ffd42181fedd02f5d20b9a5d651a90","tid":660871,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T05:28:39.000Z","msg":"物極必反就係咁既意思...希望個位媽媽明白"},{"pid":"60a7848f16c6d3c0f8c7cb2e09c721b6344f6bb6","tid":660871,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T05:31:19.000Z","msg":"惡毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好強烈既指控"},{"pid":"77d3892233c120b688222d6e41ce10ab3ee641ad","tid":660871,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T05:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac3827d9b629e7954e394513e702385b5d378d9","tid":660871,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af56239087ffd42181fedd02f5d20b9a5d651a90","tid":660871,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T05:28:39.000Z","msg":"物極必反就係咁既意思...希望個位媽媽明白"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T05:36:42.000Z","msg":"父母會以過來人身分話你唔挨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9f98351c22d6e9f2319524db032632ccf2211c","tid":660871,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T05:37:49.000Z","msg":"似係商場活動<br />\n所以佢媽應該唔知呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9591fd72192a4c76fe9584bb05191f6f2e146adb","tid":660871,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T05:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>惡毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好強烈既指控</blockquote><br />\n素雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c729ce33e2399257ffe2fbbad70b3bd35b8783ec","tid":660871,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":